# ChatterDaemon environment contract.
# config.py auto-loads this .env at startup (override=False — a value already set
# in the shell wins; a missing .env no-ops, it never crashes the spine).
#
# Order 1 (the spine) needs NO credentials — it loads watchlists and derives
# windows entirely offline. Source credentials arrive with their plugins and
# become required only at that plugin's invocation, never at spine startup.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your keys. `.env` is gitignored — never
# commit real secrets (this tree lives on /mnt/c, one `git add` from a leak).

# FINNHUB_API_KEY=...     # Finnhub company-news + US symbol universe (Order 2/4)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=...   # Haiku stance over StockTwits message bodies (Order 6/9).
#                         #   OPTIONAL: without it StockTwits still ships the zero-cost
#                         #   native Bull/Bear tag read; Haiku just doesn't run.
#
# Sources that need NO key:
#   StockTwits    — trending + symbol streams are public (browser UA).   (Order 9)
#   4chan /smg/   — public JSON API.                                     (Order 3)

# --- optional overrides (defaults in config.py) ---
# CHATTER_WATCHLISTS_DIR=...   # defaults to the watchlists/ dir beside pyproject.toml
# LOG_LEVEL=INFO
# CHATTER_SENTIMENT_MIN=3      # min StockTwits messages before Haiku runs (else native-only)
